PrecisDeclaration that the Governor in Council is of the opinion that it is in the national interest for the Minister of Industry, Science and Technology to develop and implement programs and projects of special assistance to Indians, Métis, Inuit and non-status Indians of Canada, and to legal entities owned or controlled by any of them, to aid economic development.

precis:
Declaration that the Governor in Council is of the opinion that it is in
the national interest for the Minister of Industry, Science and
Technology to develop and implement programs and projects of special
assistance to Indians, Métis, Inuit and non-status Indians of Canada, and
to legal entities owned or controlled by any of them, to aid economic
development.
